  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Transport Board's Jaffna Road Workers strike",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Transport Board's Jaffna road workers and private bus drivers (25) went on strike on Monday.",
        "Last Friday at 9:00 pm, the driver and the guard of the 57-route EPO bus that left Jaffna for Colombo were attacked by the employees of the Kalkamuwa Road EPO Road in Thaladagama, the Sri Lanka Transport Board said that appropriate action should be taken against the employees who carried out the attack. The road workers have been boycotting for the past two days.",
        "Meanwhile, Jaffna district private buses are not in local and out-of-town service due to problems in getting fuel.",
        "Due to lack of fuel to run the service, all private transport has come to a standstill and long distance bus services have not operated.",
        "Sri Lankan Transport Board buses and private buses were involved in boycotting services, and commuters faced a lot of difficulties.",
        "Especially when schools have started after a long time, students and teachers faced difficulties in going to schools."
      ],
